data.description: SHORT TERM LEASE OPTION AVAILABLE. Super cute and updated Westside home with great curb appeal. Easy access to freeway in Idaho Falls. Close to INL bus stop. This home is move in ready with many updates including all new flooring, paint and lighting. The kitchen is large with movable center island and a ton of cabinet space. There is plenty of room for a big dining room table. Main floor has a large living room and there is another large family room in the finished basement. This home has plenty of space with shelving in both the storage room and under the stairs. The back yard has a large well built insulated shed. Newer roof and furnace, A/C and large fenced yard. There is a large deck in back perfect for BBQ's and entertaining and also a garden spot. Extra parking available with two driveways and an oversized one-car garage. Pets negotiable.
